LottoDraw - Class in Unnamed Package
this is the main class of the program that simulates a lotto draw it takes LottoDraw.WINNING_NUMBERS random numbers from 1 - LottoDraw.MAX_NUMBER and then generates a pre determind amount of tickets each ticket contains LottoDraw.WINNING_NUMBERS amount of random numbers from 1 - LottoDraw.MAX_NUMBER it then checks these LottoDraw.WINNING_NUMBERS values against the winning numbers winning numbers are also generated randomly from 1 - LottoDraw.MAX_NUMBER then prints out what each ticket won based on the amount of matches they have with the winning numbers
